OL,3,CFormer footballer Kevin Campbell 'died
OL,4,Cof natural causes'
OL,6,FAn internal investigation by the
OL,7,Fhospital accepted the infection -
OL,8,Fcaused by bacteria entering the blood
OL,9,Fand travelling to the heart - could
OL,10,Fhave been diagnosed earlier and that
OL,11,F"more curiosity" should have been
OL,12,Fshown by clinicians over Campbell's
OL,13,Fsignificant weight loss.
OL,15,FBut the inquest was also told that he
OL,16,Fwould "almost certainly" not been been
OL,17,Ffit enough to undertake "high risk"
OL,18,Fopen-heart surgery if the infection
OL,19,Fhad been detected earlier during his
OL,20,Ffinal admission.
