OL,3,CFormer footballer Kevin Campbell 'died
OL,4,Cof natural causes'
OL,6,FRecording a conclusion of death by
OL,7,Fnatural causes, Golombek said: "Kevin
OL,8,Fdied from a naturally occurring
OL,9,Fillness which very sadly on 15 June
OL,10,Freached its natural end."
OL,12,FCampbell scored 59 goals in 224 games
OL,13,Ffor Arsenal and, alongside the 1990-91
OL,14,Fleague title, also won the FA Cup,
OL,15,FLeague Cup and European Cup Winners'
OL,16,FCup with the Gunners.
OL,18,FHe also played for Nottingham Forest,
OL,19,FTrabzonspor, Everton, West Brom and
OL,20,FCardiff.
